sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Cliente/Aplicación
    participant ProxyREST as RollbackPurchaseRestPS
    participant ProxySoap as RollbackPurchaseSoapPS
    participant Pipeline as RollbackPurchasePP
    participant Template as HondurasCardTemplate
    participant LogService as LoggingRegionalRestBS
    participant DBGetTicket as DBGetStatusTicketAdapter
    participant OracleDB as Oracle DB (PagosWSTC)
    participant VisionPlus as Vision+ OnlineTransactions
    participant DBActTicket as DBActTicketAdapter
    participant ErrorService as GetCustomErrorByStackTraceRegionalRestBS

    Note over Client, ErrorService: Flujo Honduras (HN01) - RollbackPurchase

    alt Request REST
        Client->>ProxyREST: POST /honduras/card/rest/rollbackPurchase/v1
        Note right of Client: Content-Type: application/json<br/>Authorization: Basic Auth<br/>HTTPS
        ProxyREST->>Pipeline: Invoke Pipeline
    else Request SOAP
        Client->>ProxySoap: POST /honduras/card/soap/rollbackPurchase/v1
        Note right of Client: SOAP 1.1<br/>Authorization: Basic Auth<br/>HTTPS
        ProxySoap->>Pipeline: Invoke Pipeline
    end

    Pipeline->>Pipeline: Validar Esquema XML/JSON
    Note right of Pipeline: Validar campos obligatorios:<br/>- GeneralInfo<br/>- Ticket<br/>- TransactionType

    Pipeline->>Template: Apply HondurasCardTemplate
    Template->>Template: StageAssigment
    Note right of Template: Asignar variables:<br/>service = "Card/RollbackPurchase"<br/>version = "v1"<br/>key = "Ticket"<br/>value = data(Ticket)<br/>method = "SOAP"<br/>operationTargetSystem = "ReversaPagoTarjeta"<br/>targetSystem = "Vision+"

    Template->>LogService: SaveLogInFileSystem (REQUEST)
    Note right of Template: Transformación: ServiceToLog.xqy<br/>Registrar request de entrada<br/>GlobalId, SourceBank, Ticket
    LogService-->>Template: Log guardado

    Pipeline->>Pipeline: Transform: RollbackPurchaseToPagosWS.xqy
    Note right of Pipeline: Mapeo OSB → BD:<br/>Ticket → PV_TICKET

    Pipeline->>DBGetTicket: Invoke DBGetStatusTicketAdapter
    Note right of Pipeline: Operation: DBGetStatusTicketAdapter

    DBGetTicket->>OracleDB: CALL OSB_CONS_BROKER_RECAUDO_TICKET
    Note right of DBGetTicket: Schema: PAGOSWSTC<br/>Package: OSB_K_RECAUDO_BROKER_HN<br/>IN: PV_TICKET<br/>OUT: 29 campos (estado, tarjeta, monto, etc.)

    alt Ticket No Encontrado
        OracleDB-->>DBGetTicket: PV_SUCCESSINDICATOR != 'SUCCESS'
        DBGetTicket-->>Pipeline: Response con error
        Pipeline->>Pipeline: Asignar codeErrorService = 'ERROR'
        Pipeline->>ErrorService: GetCustomErrorByStackTrace
        Note right of Pipeline: Transformación: ServicesToError.xqy<br/>systemApplication = 'PAGOSWSTC'<br/>errorCode = PV_SUCCESSINDICATOR<br/>errorMessage = PV_MESSAGES
        ErrorService-->>Pipeline: Error mapeado
        Pipeline->>Pipeline: Transform: ErrorToRollbackPurchase.xqy
        Note right of Pipeline: Construir response de error<br/>con ErrorInfo completo
        Pipeline->>LogService: SaveLogInFileSystem (ERROR)
        LogService-->>Pipeline: Log guardado
        Pipeline-->>Client: Response con Error
    end

    OracleDB-->>DBGetTicket: ResultSet con datos del ticket
    Note left of OracleDB: PV_SUCCESSINDICATOR = 'SUCCESS'<br/>PV_MESSAGES = ''<br/>PV_ESTADO_TICKET<br/>PV_NUMEROTARJETA<br/>PN_ORGANIZACION<br/>PV_MERCHANTNUMBER<br/>PN_VALOREFECTIVO<br/>PV_FECHAEXPTC<br/>PV_SECUENCIAMOVIMIENTO<br/>(+ 22 campos más)

    DBGetTicket-->>Pipeline: Response exitoso
    Pipeline->>Pipeline: Validar respuesta
    Note right of Pipeline: Condición:<br/>codeErrorGetTicket = 'SUCCESS'<br/>AND messageErrorService = ''

    alt Validación Fallida
        Pipeline->>Pipeline: Asignar codeErrorService = 'ERROR'
        Pipeline->>ErrorService: GetCustomErrorByStackTrace
        ErrorService-->>Pipeline: Error mapeado
        Pipeline->>Pipeline: Transform: ErrorToRollbackPurchase.xqy
        Pipeline->>LogService: SaveLogInFileSystem (ERROR)
        LogService-->>Pipeline: Log guardado
        Pipeline-->>Client: Response con Error
    end

    Pipeline->>Pipeline: Transform: RollbackPurchaseToOnlinePayment.xqy
    Note right of Pipeline: Mapeo Ticket → Vision+:<br/>POSUserData = 'ATX'<br/>RRN37 = YYDDDHHMMssssss (generado)<br/>NumberOfInstallments = '00'<br/>MCCType = '6010'<br/>RequestType = 'R' (Reversal)<br/>CardNumber = PV_NUMEROTARJETA<br/>OrgId = PN_ORGANIZACION<br/>MerchantNumber = PV_MERCHANTNUMBER<br/>CardExpirationDate = PV_FECHAEXPTC<br/>TotalSalesAmount = PN_VALOREFECTIVO<br/>Track2Length = '0000'<br/>Track2Data = '0000'<br/>CardValidationValue = '000'

    Pipeline->>VisionPlus: Invoke OnlineUpdateCard
    Note right of Pipeline: Endpoint: http://172.28.1.145:7802/OTWS/v4<br/>Operation: OnlineUpdateCard<br/>Timeout: 70s<br/>Connection Timeout: 65s

    VisionPlus->>VisionPlus: Procesar reversión de compra
    Note right of VisionPlus: Validar tarjeta<br/>Validar monto<br/>Ejecutar reversión en Vision+

    alt Reversión Rechazada por Vision+
        VisionPlus-->>Pipeline: ActionDescription != 'APPROVED'
        Note left of VisionPlus: Ejemplos:<br/>- DECLINED<br/>- INSUFFICIENT_FUNDS<br/>- INVALID_CARD
        Pipeline->>Pipeline: Asignar statusService = 'ERROR'
        Pipeline->>Pipeline: Asignar codeErrorService = 'ERROR'
        Pipeline->>ErrorService: GetCustomErrorByStackTrace
        ErrorService-->>Pipeline: Error mapeado
        Pipeline->>Pipeline: Transform: ErrorToRollbackPurchase.xqy
        Note right of Pipeline: messaggeOnlinePayment = ActionDescription
        Pipeline->>LogService: SaveLogInFileSystem (ERROR)
        LogService-->>Pipeline: Log guardado
        Pipeline-->>Client: Response con Error
    end

    VisionPlus-->>Pipeline: Response exitoso
    Note left of VisionPlus: POSUserData = 'ATX'<br/>RRN37 = (mismo enviado)<br/>VPrespCode = '00'<br/>SystemAction = 'APPROVE'<br/>ReasonActionCode = 0<br/>ActionDescription = 'APPROVED'<br/>CardValidationResult = 'PASS'<br/>AuthorizationCode = 'AUTH123456'

    Pipeline->>Pipeline: Validar respuesta Vision+
    Note right of Pipeline: Condición:<br/>fn-bea:trim(ActionDescription) = 'APPROVED'

    Pipeline->>Pipeline: Transform: RollbackPurchaseToActTicket.xqy
    Note right of Pipeline: Mapeo OSB → BD:<br/>Ticket → PV_TICKET<br/>statusTicket = 'R' → PV_ESTADO_TICKET

    Pipeline->>DBActTicket: Invoke DBActTicketAdapter
    Note right of Pipeline: Operation: DBActTicketAdapter

    DBActTicket->>OracleDB: CALL OSB_ACT_BROKER_RECAUDO_TICKET
    Note right of DBActTicket: Schema: PAGOSWSTC<br/>Package: OSB_K_RECAUDO_BROKER_HN<br/>IN: PV_TICKET, PV_ESTADO_TICKET='R'<br/>OUT: PV_SUCCESSINDICATOR, PV_MESSAGES

    alt Actualización Fallida
        OracleDB-->>DBActTicket: PV_SUCCESSINDICATOR != 'SUCCESS'
        DBActTicket-->>Pipeline: Response con error
        Pipeline->>Pipeline: Asignar statusService = 'ERROR'
        Pipeline->>Pipeline: Asignar codeErrorService = 'ERROR'
        Pipeline->>ErrorService: GetCustomErrorByStackTrace
        ErrorService-->>Pipeline: Error mapeado
        Pipeline->>Pipeline: Transform: ErrorToRollbackPurchase.xqy
        Pipeline->>LogService: SaveLogInFileSystem (ERROR)
        LogService-->>Pipeline: Log guardado
        Pipeline-->>Client: Response con Error
    end

    OracleDB-->>DBActTicket: PV_SUCCESSINDICATOR = 'SUCCESS'
    Note left of OracleDB: Ticket actualizado a estado 'R'<br/>PV_MESSAGES = ''

    DBActTicket-->>Pipeline: Response exitoso

    Pipeline->>Pipeline: Validar actualización
    Note right of Pipeline: Condición:<br/>codeErrorService = 'SUCCESS'

    Pipeline->>Pipeline: Transform: PagosWSToRollbackPurchase.xqy
    Note right of Pipeline: Construir response exitoso:<br/>StatusInfo/Status = 'SUCCESS'<br/>StatusInfo/ValueDate = current-date<br/>StatusInfo/DateTime = current-dateTime<br/>StatusInfo/GlobalId = (del request)

    Pipeline->>LogService: SaveLogInFileSystem (RESPONSE)
    Note right of Pipeline: Registrar response exitoso
    LogService-->>Pipeline: Log guardado

    Pipeline-->>Client: Response exitoso
    Note left of Client: StatusInfo/Status = 'SUCCESS'<br/>ErrorInfo vacío<br/>Datos del ticket reversado

    Note over Client, ErrorService: Transformaciones Clave:
    Note over Client, ErrorService: 1. RollbackPurchaseToPagosWS.xqy: OSB → Consulta BD
    Note over Client, ErrorService: 2. RollbackPurchaseToOnlinePayment.xqy: Ticket → Vision+ (con RRN37 generado)
    Note over Client, ErrorService: 3. RollbackPurchaseToActTicket.xqy: OSB → Actualización BD (estado='R')
    Note over Client, ErrorService: 4. PagosWSToRollbackPurchase.xqy: BD → OSB Response (éxito)
    Note over Client, ErrorService: 5. ErrorToRollbackPurchase.xqy: Error → OSB Response (error)

    Note over Client, ErrorService: Validaciones Críticas:
    Note over Client, ErrorService: 1. Ticket existe: PV_SUCCESSINDICATOR='SUCCESS' AND PV_MESSAGES=''
    Note over Client, ErrorService: 2. Reversión aprobada: trim(ActionDescription)='APPROVED'
    Note over Client, ErrorService: 3. Actualización exitosa: PV_SUCCESSINDICATOR='SUCCESS'

    Note over Client, ErrorService: Retry Policies:
    Note over Client, ErrorService: - DBGetTicket: 4 reintentos, 1-120s, backoff=2
    Note over Client, ErrorService: - DBActTicket: 4 reintentos, 1-120s, backoff=2
    Note over Client, ErrorService: - Vision+: 0 reintentos, timeout=70s
